Yes, this line was added in the commit. The previous version of the function 'skip_insignificant_space' did not include this line. The older version of the function is:
```c
static gboolean skip_insignificant_space (const char *resource, int *pos, int resource_length) {
    while ((resource[*pos] == '\t') ||
           (resource[*pos] == ' ') ||
           (resource[*pos] == '\n')) {
        (*pos)++;
    }
    return FALSE;
}
```

